Credit Card Recommendation Chatbot

A smart, conversational credit card advisor built with recommendation engine. Users can chat with the assistant to get personalized credit card suggestions based on income, spending, perks, and credit score.

Features

- Chat-based UI with step-by-step input collection
- AI-driven assistant powered by LangChain (LLM or mock fallback)
- Real-time credit card recommendation using a static card dataset
- Reward simulation and benefit estimation
- Post-chat summary and comparison view
- Fully responsive design using Tailwind CSS
- Backend API via FastAPI
